Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.33,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Lovely Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,完美一跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了这件服装  多亏了翔的灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爱良也让我的作品闪耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大家  上吧
